            {
                "comment": "Lackluster professor. Has that &quot;I know more than you&quot; attitude towards students in office hours. Programming assignments ended up being 3000+ lines long near the end of the semester. Homeworks are difficult and tricky if you aren't on TOP of everything in this class. Midterm was absolute hell, really the hardest thing I've ever taken..",
